(446, 26, 1, '', '2017-09-29 04:41:51', 957, 2940, 'bd73c07c3dd5ff2a63f4627610ba1c33fb4c5cf4', '{"id":26,"asset_id":353,"title":"Mangkai Island","alias":"mangkai-island","introtext":"<p>Mangkai Island is one of the outermost islands that located in the group of Anambas Islands. This hilly island has white sandy beaches and rocky land. The island is inhabited only by the lighthouse keeper and the Navy. There is also a small Mangkai island in smaller size next to Mangkai Island. Administratively, this islands are part to the area of Keramut village, Jemaja districts, Natuna Regency, Riau Islands province. The island is located in the Natuna Sea and it borders to Malaysia.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2><strong>How to get there:<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>To access Mangkai Island, we can depart from Batam to Palmatak, which is the capital of Matak Island by small plane. Then, continue by renting a speedboat to Letung, the capital of Jemaja districts. Then, we can rent another medium-sized motorboat to reach Mangkai Island for about 1 hour and 30 minutes.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>In addition, the trip can also be reached by ferry which departed from Tanjungpinang. These ferry boats operate every four days, of which KM. Bukit Raya and KM. Lawit. From Tanjungpinang, the ship will directly leave for Letung -Tarempa and Natuna. It will take approximately 8 hours.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"28","created":"2017-09-29 04:41:51","created_by":"957","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2017-09-29 04:41:51","modified_by":null,"checked_out":null,"checked_out_time":null,"publish_up":"2017-09-29 04:41:51","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_associations\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_page_title\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":1,"ordering":null,"metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":null,"metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0);
